cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use onnx2coreml in your work, please cite it using these metadata."
title: "onnx2coreml: Convert ONNX models to Apple Core ML"
abstract: >-
  onnx2coreml converts ONNX models to Apple Core ML (.mlpackage / ML Program and
  .mlmodel / NeuralNetwork), built on coremltools' MIL builder, with
  numerical-parity verification against ONNX Runtime.
type: software
version: "1.1.0"
date-released: "2026-06-17"
authors:
